===========================================================================
README:  This file describes the contents of this repo and its intended use
Author:  Jack Eubanks
Date:    6/14/2024
===========================================================================


Compiling Requirements:
----------------------------
- A C++ compiler which supports C++ 11 (or higher version)


Contents of this repo:
-------------------------
1. "dlist.h" - Defines a template class which can be used to implement a doubly-linked list.
2. "LinkedListTest.cpp" - Test program for the doubly-linked list class, DList.
3. "README" - (this file)




